CatDescriptText: image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 13, 1959, pg. A16, reads: "Junior Aides - A new innovation for D.I.'s was the addition of junior aides as [to] their "Atlantic City U.S.A. review Sunday. Above are Paquita Sharp, Dole Ritter, Sylvia Davis, and Juanita Craxter."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of four D. I. Club Junior Aides, from left: Paquita Sharp, Dole Ritter, Sylvia Davis, and Joanita Craxter, posed around light colored cabinet in Gloria Grate's home, in preparation for the D.I.'s "Atlantic City U.S.A." revue held in the Press Room of the Hotel Sherwyn
